TRAMA: The telling of the story of Solomon Northup, an African American violinist kidnapped and sold as a slave in the southern United States.
A powerful virus that turns people into murderers escapes from an English research laboratory. In 28 days the epidemic is rampant and the survivors gather to flee the city.

Following their grandfather to Japan, the three children are chased by a trio of zany thieves and an army of perfectly trained ninjas. Rocky, Colt and Tam Tam are overwhelmed by the acrobatic action and irrepressible comedy.
Rocky, Colt and Tum Tum, three wild boys, find themselves embroiled in a dispute between an Indian tribe and a ruthless businessman who has used the community's territories as a landfill.

TITOLO: 3 Ninja 4 High Noon at Mega Mountain
TRAMA: Three ninja brothers travel to Mega Mountain amusement park, where they want to meet their television idol, Dave Dragon. However, on that very day, the diabolical Medusa takes over the park with her strength.
Each year, three brothers visit their grandfather for the summer. He is highly skilled in ninjutsu, and for years he has trained the boys in his techniques.
The return of Themistocles against the massive invasion by the Persian forces, led by the man transformed into a god, Xerxes, and by Artemisia, the vengeful commander of the Persian navy.

Originally released to regional audiences, this biographical drama presents an intimate look at the Pettys, who achieved fame and success in the stock-car-racing world. Action-packed racing scenes alternate with looks at the personal conflicts between Richard Petty and his father Lee.
Japan, 18th century: forty-seven samurai want to avenge the death of their master, killed by an evil tyrant.
Disney's adaptation of the famous Dickens novel. Old Scrooge, an insensitive and miserly rich, has to deal with the spirit of the past, present and future to understand the joys of sharing.

Compilation of eight segments tied to Christmas or winter in some small or big way from eight Disney features and shorts. Between the segments shots from Disneyland and of Disney toys are shown while narrators sing about the next clip.

Two dim-witted brothers dream of owning their own dance club or at least getting into the coolest and most exclusive club in town, The Roxbury. The Roxbury Guys, Steve and Doug Butabi, want to get into the best club in town, and also hope to open their own club.
The monstrous spirit of a slain child murderer seeks revenge by invading the dreams of teenagers whose parents were responsible for his untimely death.

TITOLO: A Nightmare on Elm Street 2  Freddy's Revenge
TRAMA: A teenage boy is haunted in his dreams by deceased child murderer Freddy Krueger, who is out to possess him in order to continue his reign of terror in the real world.

TITOLO: A Nightmare on Elm Street 3  Dream Warriors
TRAMA: A psychiist familiar with knife-wielding dream demon Freddy Krueger helps teens at a mental hospital battle the killer who is invading their dreams.

TITOLO: A Nightmare on Elm Street 4  The Dream Master
TRAMA: The monstrous spirit of a slain child murderer seeks revenge by invading the dreams of teenagers whose parents were responsible for his untimely death.

A ranger and his son, from the planet Nova Prime, are on their way in their spacecraft when they are forced to make an emergency landing on Earth, which has become a wilderness dominated by strange creatures.
When Charlotte Sutter is kidnapped by Apaches, her brother Sam, aided by an old drunk prospector, goes searching for her.
he story of the life and career of Muhammad Ali. The boxing champion has shown determination, physical endurance and intelligence, becoming a living legend in the American boxing world.

A couple traveling through a backwoods area are held by a a group of orphans who want them to become their parents. Unfortunately, the kids have a habit of killing adults who refuse that pacular honor.
Student Peter Parker's life is turned upside down by the arrival of dangerous new opponents. As Spider-Man, he must protect loved ones and New York City from this deadly threat.

New York, 1970s. The true story of Frank Lucas, a drug dealer who, following the death of his boss, manages to become the most famous drug dealer in America. Meanwhile, cop Richie Roberts tries to catch him.
An ambitious FBI agent forces two cheating experts to infiltrate the New Jersey mafia.
Ron Burgundy tries to ride the wave when he and his team agree to work for one of the first broadcasters that broadcasts 24 hours a day.

TITOLO: Anchorman: The Legend of Ron Burgundy
TRAMA: Anchorman: The Legend of Ron Burgundy is a 2004 American comedy film directed by Adam McKay, produced by Judd Apatow, starring Will Ferrell, and written by McKay and Ferrell. The film is a tongue-in-cheek take on the culture of the 1970s, pacularly the new Action News format.It portrays a San Diego TV station where Ferrell's title character clashes with his new female counterpart.
The archivist of a police station becomes the guinea pig of a bizarre experiment and is transformed into a walking zoo.
The animal kingdom stages its own olympic games.
Many years after the death of their daughter, a toymaker and his wife welcome a nun and six girls from an orphanage into their home. But Annabelle, a doll possessed by a demon, begins to attack them.
In the western desert a young brave avenges the deaths of his tribe in a massacre by the US Army.

Arnold (1973) Upon his death, Arnold marries his lover, Karen, in spite of his widow, and leaves deathtraps accompanied by audiotapes and his preserved and aculate corpse for those who cared only for his money.

TITOLO: Austin Powers: International Man of Mystery
TRAMA: Thirty years later, in 1997, Dr. Evil returns to discover his henchman Number 2 has developed Virtucon, the legitimate front of Evil's empire, into a multibillion-dollar enterprise. Uninterested in business, Dr. Evil conspires to steal nuclear weapons and hold the world hostage for $1 million.

TITOLO: Austin Powers: The Spy Who Shagged Me
TRAMA: During the honeymoon, secret agent Austin Powers discovers that Dr. Male has taken a journey back in time to retrieve the mojo, an aphrodisiac herb potion. With Felicity's help, the man returns to the 1960s.
Two hip detectives protect a witness to a murder while investigating a case of stolen heroin from the evidence storage room from their police precinct.

Eight years after the events of the first film, Miami Police Department (MPD) narcotic investigators Marcus Burnett and Mike Lowrey are studying the flow of MDMA into the city, leading them to a meeting with the KKK and drug discontinuation. The subsequent raid failed due to weak radio signals, and in the gunfight in which several Klan members are killed or injured, Mike accidentally shoots Marcus in the buttocks. The MPD arrests the surviving members of the Klan, who turn out to be mere small buyers and not distributors of ecstasy.
Irving Zisman, an eighty-six year old grandfather, travels through America with his grandson to allow him to meet his real father. Together they create a series of crazy and self-injurious gags.
Showing the life(dramatic) of the hot boys or cash money millionaires and how it goes down in the magnolia,dirty cops,drug life and shootouts with a twist of reality

TITOLO: Battle For The Planet Of The Apes
TRAMA: Ten years after a worldwide series of ape revolutions and a brutal nuclear war among humans, Caesar must protect survivors of both species from an insidious human cult and a militant ape faction alike.
Battle of the Year - Victory is at stake is a 2013 film directed by Benson Lee. The film is based on the documentary Planet B-Boy, winner of the Lee Award in 2008, which portrayed the competition ...
In 1999 Queens, New York City, young street criminals Tommy "Buns" Bundy (DMX) and Sincere ("Sin") (Nas), along with associates Mark and Black, murder five people during a violent nightclub robbery.
An astronaut, on a journey to find a missing colleague, comes into contact with an underground civilization made up of humans with telepathic powers who worship a nuclear weapon.

TITOLO: Beneath the Planet of the Apes
TRAMA: The sole survivor of an interplanetary rescue mission searches for the only survivor of the previous expedition. He discovers a planet ruled by apes and an underground city run by telepathic humans.

Isabel Bigelow is a young witch who has decided to live a normal life, to find a job, friends and love, like ordinary mortals. One day, while in a coffee shop, she is noticed by the famous actor Jack Wyatt, enchanted by the way she wrinkles her nose, who offers her a job as an interpreter of Samantha in the remake of the TV series Vita da witch. Isabel, falling in love with the actor, accepts, but discovers that she wants to use it only to find the lost success. Eventually Jack, realizing Isabel's talent, gives her a real part; in the meantime a story arises between the two that becomes complicated when she reveals that she is actually a witch.
Blade, born half man and half vampire, possesses more powers than any human being or creature of darkness.
The vampire hunter Blade makes an alliance with his usual opponents, to fight together a powerful common enemy: Jared Nomak, of the powerful breed of reapers.

Vampires manage to frame Blade (battle name of their most fearful hunter), blaming him for the death of a human (a "family member" dressed up as a vampire), a killing that occurred after a car chase. Blade, filmed on television and wanted by the FBI, is tracked down in his refuge. His mentor and friend, Abraham Whistler, then detonates the entire building, sacrificing himself to protect the secrets and true identity of Blade (whose name is Eric Brooks, born of a pregnant woman, half vampire, nicknamed the "Diurnal" for its ability to withstand sunlight).
Two ice skating champions, and great rivals, are disqualified from individual competitions due to a fight. In order to compete, they have only one solution: to register as a couple.
Based on the true life experiences of poet Jimmy Santiago Baca, the film focuses on step-brothers Paco and Cruz, and their bi-racial cousin Miklo.
In the midst of a searing Florida heat wave, a woman persuades her lover, a small-town lawyer, to murder her rich husband.

A man moves to Los Angeles seeking fame and fortune but ends up wearing a dinosaur costume at the Hollywood and Highland Mall taking photos with tourists for tips. After foiling the hi jacking of a Metro bus in his costume by accident a college student decides to feature the costumed hero in her final school project, a documentary.
A smart-mouthed junkie and loser known as J.J. (George Segal) spends his days looking for just "one more fix".
Accused of murder by some CIA agents on a mission, Jason Bourne is forced to return to the field and resume his past as a trained spy to kill.

Jason Bourne is back. His anguish is always fueled by the need to know who and why has transformed him into a machine to kill by erasing his identity. Added to this is the desire to avenge the death of his partner.

Outcome's agent, Aaron Cross, who survived the closure of the program, or the physical elimination of all its components, must detoxify the medicines he was forced to take to improve his physical performance.

A man is torn from death by the intervention of the crew of an Italian fishing boat in the Mediterranean Sea and discovers that he has become the target of some hit men. Man does not remember anything about himself.
Follows the lives of three young males living in the Crenshaw ghetto of Los Angeles, dissecting questions of race, relationships, violence and future prospects.
A hunting vacation goes horribly awry for 4 friends after they accidentally shoot the lease's land owner.
Bugs Bunny reflects on his past cartoon exploits.

Cabin by the Lake. Cabin by the Lake is a horror TV movie released in 2000. It tells the story of Stanley, played by Judd Nelson, a script writer who begins killing girls for research for a movie he is writing, where the villain does the same thing.

Carrie is a young girl with many complexes, who is made fun of by schoolmates and has a mother with a problematic personality. At the same time, however, she is a little girl with an extraordinary and terrifying power, which gradually transforms her into a machine of death and destruction.
The Lambert family is convinced that they have won the battle against evil spirits, but must soon change their mind.
An aspiring painter compromises his ambition for his seductive girlfriend, only to be torn when his empowering, new muse reignites his passion.
A single mother gives her son a much sought-after doll for his birthday, only to discover that it is possessed by the soul of a serial killer.
While Andy's mother is admitted to a psychiic hospital, the young boy is placed in foster care, and Chucky, determined to claim Andy's soul, is not far behind.
Chucky returns for revenge against Andy, the young boy who defeated him, and now a teenager living in a military academy.
A young couple is trapped in a remote town where a dangerous religious cult of children believes that everyone over age 18 must be killed.

TITOLO: Children of the Corn 666 VI: Isaac's Return
TRAMA: Children of the Corn 666: Isaac's Return (1999) As a teenage girl comes to Gatlin to find her biological mother, the town's infamous cult plots a comeback as their leader, Isaac, awakens from a coma.

TITOLO: Children of the Corn II: The Final Sacrifice
TRAMA: A journalist and his son travel to Nebraska to investigate the mysterious town of Gatlin where, unbeknownst to them, a murderous cult of children are still waiting in the corn fields

TITOLO: Children of the Corn III: Urban Harvest
TRAMA: As a teenage girl comes to Gatlin to find her biological mother, the town's infamous cult plots a comeback as their leader, Isaac, awakens from a coma. A young couple is trapped in a remote town where a dangerous religious cult of children believes that everyone over age 18 must be killed.

TITOLO: Children of the Corn IV: The Gathering
TRAMA: The plot follows a medical student returning to her hometown in Nebraska, where she finds the children to be falling under a mysterious mass illness connected to the town's past. The film expands upon the origins of "He Who Walks Behind the Rows".

TITOLO: Children of the Corn V: Fields of Terror
TRAMA: Six college boys, mistaking the road, find themselves in a place called Divinity Falls. The atmosphere is very disturbing and, when they are about to leave the place, they discover that the children of the village are controlled by an evil force that leads them to exterminate adults. The plot is the same as the whole saga "Children of the corn" (Blood red wheat) taken from the famous story by Master Stephen King.
A valedictorian and a juvenile delinquent have their school records switched and begin to be treated like the other.
An experienced cop and his rookie partner pol the streets of East Los Angeles while trying to keep the gang violence under control.
Will Eubanks (Tom Selleck) and his rowdy gambling buddy J.D. Reed (Jerry Reed) are two good-time roustabouts. After being caught in a sting card game, the two men are forced to leave town in a hurry.
When an expedition to the African Congo ends in disaster, a new team is assembled to find out what went wrong.

TITOLO: Conquest Of The Planet Of The Apes
TRAMA: In a futuristic world that has embraced ape slavery, Caesar, the son of the late simians Cornelius and Zira, surfaces after almost twenty years of hiding out from the authorities, and prepares for a slave revolt against humanity.

The wealthy Hulot family gathers at the deathbed of their mon Adeline (Geraldine Chaplin). Adeline's husband, the Baron Hector Hulot (Hugh Laurie) has squandered their fortune on an extravagant string of mistresses and plunged them heavily into debt, a fact which stresses the entire family.
On a U.S. nuclear missile sub, a young First Officer stages a mutiny to prevent his trigger happy Captain from launching his missiles before confirming his orders to do so.
Cujo, a friendly St. Bernard, contracts rabies and conducts a reign of terror on a small American town.
Original film was called "Teenagers Battle the Thing" made in 1958. Approximately 59 minutes.
Can Gordon's team win the Junior Goodwill Games in California in spite of all the set-backs?

Havana, 1958. During the communist revolution led by Fidel Castro, an American high school student, Katey Miller, moved to the Caribbean island with her family. Here he meets the Cuban Javier Suarez, waiter of the hotel where he is staying. Javier is in a difficult economic situation, so Katey decides to help him by entering a dance competition with him. The prize consists of a ticket to the United States and $ 5,000. The two have some problems at the beginning, she is very rigid in her steps, he is free, but the feeling infiltrates them. They don't win the race, but their love blossoms in passion, on the days when the island is freed. Katie is forced to leave Javier and Cuba herself after an evening of dance and joy.
An ex-Marine turned teacher struggles to connect with her students in an inner city school.
A Vietnam vet adjusts to life after the war while trying to support his family, but the chance of a better life may involve crime and bloodshed.
An evil Oriental Dragon Lady injects three maal arts fighters with a serum that turns them into zombie-like assassins, and she sends them out against her enemies.
A jazz pianist and a wisecracking journalist are pulled into a complex web of mystery after the former witnesses the brutal murder of a psychic.

On planet Earth, a galaxy alliance was formed. Together with the good planets of the solar system, they maintained peace throughout the universe. Until a new horrible menace threatened the galaxy and Voltron was needed once more.
Following a serious terrorist attack, Special Agent Doug Carlin is instructed to hunt down the perpetrator using experimental technology that allows him to travel through time.

David Wozniack is an affable man who works as a bellman for the family business. His life proceeds calmly and without great ambitions until he discovers he is the biological father of more than five hundred children. Many of them have filed a lawsuit to be able to know his identity.
A criminal decides to quit the past and become a policeman. When he realizes that violence and corruption are in the police too, he is faced with a dangerous choice.
Spending the summer at a Catskills resort with her family, Frances "Baby" Houseman falls in love with the camp's dance instructor, Johnny Castle.

Django Unchained is a 2012 film written and directed by Quentin Tarantino, starring Jamie Foxx, Christoph Waltz, Leonardo DiCaprio, Kerry Washington and Samuel L. Jackson. It is a tribute to the 1966 film Django directed by Sergio Corbucci and starring Franco Nero, who appears in a cameo in this film.
A descendant of Jesus has the task of stopping two fallen angels who want to destroy the world.

TITOLO: Don't Be a Menace to South Central While Drinking Your Juice in the Hood
TRAMA: A parody of several U.S. films about being in the 'Hood', for instance "Boyz n the Hood", "South Central", "Menace II Society", "Higher Learning" and "Juice".

TITOLO: Don't Tell Mom the Babysitter's Dead
TRAMA: Five siblings are left alone all summer when their mom leaves town and the evil babysitter bites the dust.

Spies discover that the Red Chinese have built a "doomsday machine" capable of destroying the surface of the Earth, and that they plan to use it within a matter of days. Meanwhile, Project Astra, a manned U.S. space mission to Venus, is in its final hours before launch when it is taken over by the military and nearly half of its all-male crew is replaced by women. The reason for this becomes apparent when, shortly after Astra leaves orbit, the Earth is completely destroyed in a global cataclysm! Is the human race doomed? What dangers and wonders await the crew of the Astra on their journey to Venus?

TITOLO: Dragon Ball Z: Fusion  Last Saiyan
TRAMA: In the Other World, a teenage "oni" guarding a spirit cleansing machine turns the volume of his walkman up so loud that he fails to change the evil essence tank when necessary. Due to the overload of evil essence, the machine explodes and the "oni" is transformed into a huge-childlike monster with power over the laws regarding the worlds of the living and the dead. As a result, both worlds are thrown into chaos: in the living world, several deceased are brought back to life, while in the other world, beings who were allowed to keep their bodies turn into spirits, and vice versa.

An ast slowly goes insane while struggling to pay his bills, work on his paintings, and care for his two female roommates, which leads him taking to the streets of New York after dark and randomly killing derelicts with a power drill.

TITOLO: Duck Tales the Movie: Treasure of the Lost Lamp
TRAMA: Scrooge McDuck takes Huey, Dewey, and Louie to Egypt to find a pyramid and magic lamp.

A man, adopted years earlier by one of Santa's elves, after being mistakenly transported to the North Pole when he was still a child, leaves the toy workshop and travels to New York to find his family.

In 2154 the rich live in the luxury of the Elysium space station while the rest of humanity barely survives on Earth. A worker, who has nothing more to lose, decides to rebel to give life to a new beginning.
New York, 1982: A security guard gets help from a childhood friend to set up a robbery of fifteen million collars.
A boy is selected due to his talent for advanced military training. His job is to lead all Earth forces in a grueling battle against an alien attack.
Robert Clayton Dean is a brilliant Washington D.C. attorney. who unbeknownst to him comes into possession of a video that charges a senior National Security Agency executive in political murder.
Magically transported to a secret universe, a girl joins the ongoing battle between good and evil, the fate of the world at stake.
Eragon is a boy of humble origins whose destiny changes radically thanks to the discovery of a dragon egg.

TITOLO: Escape From The Planet Of The Apes
TRAMA: The world is shocked by the appearance of three talking chimpanzees, who arrived mysteriously in a U.S. spacecraft. They become the toast of society, but one man believes them to be a threat to the human race.
Security expert must escape from a secret prison to find out the flaws in the system. He risks his life in his latest venture, the maximum security secret penitentiary called 'the Tomb'.

Everything Must Go (2010) When an alcoholic relapses, causing him to lose his wife and his job, he holds a yard sale on his front lawn in an attempt to start over. A new neighbor might be the key to his return to form.
The police investigate some crimes whose execution method looks strikingly similar to that used by a newly killed serial killer.
In Rio de Janeiro, former crook Dom Toretto and former police officer Brian O 'Conner join forces to confront a wealthy businessman who wants them both dead.

Agent Hobbs is chasing a criminal organization made up of experienced mercenary pilots. To frame them, he will ask Dom's team, in constant flight after having hit a millionaire hit, to beat them on the road.
Vin Diesel and Paul Walker return to star together in the fourth installment of the saga: Brian must work with the FBI to frame a trafficker with a passion for racing.

To investigate a number of thefts, policeman Brian O'Connor becomes an undercover infiltrator in the Los Angeles underground racing world. While trying to gain the boss's trust, the man risks being exposed.

TITOLO: Fast and The Furious 3 Tokyo Drift
TRAMA: Shaun Boswell is a restless guy who likes to participate in clandestine car racing. Finished in trouble with the justice system, he is forced, to avoid prison, to join his father who is a soldier serving in Tokyo.
Stripped of his badge, Officer O'Conner is recruited by the FBI to infiltrate a clandestine car racing loop in Miami and dismantle a criminal organization.

Marlin, a clown fish, is looking for his son Nemo, kidnapped by a fisherman on the coral reef. A desperate travel companion named Dory joins the desperate father. Meanwhile, the little one plans to escape from the aquarium in which he was locked up.
Whip, a pilot with severe alcoholism, makes a difficult emergency landing, becoming a hero. The investigation into the causes of the accident, however, causes his secret to come out.
Thanks to a strange invention, a forgetful professor is the only one able to save the school where he works from bankruptcy.
A woman is tormented by strange dreams of astronauts on the moon. She visits a deserted seaside town whose inhabitants know her even though she does not know them.
When their adopted mother is gunned down in a store robbery the 'four brothers' investigated the murder for themselves & look for the killers but not all is what it seems.
Dream-haunting Freddy Krueger returns once again to prowl the nightmares of Springwood's last surviving teenager, and of a woman whose personal connection to Krueger may mean his doom.

A group of turkeys travel back in time to 1621 to change the Thanksgiving tradition. Two of them, with opposite characters, are forced to put aside their contrasts and their differences to make a team.

Free Fall is a 2014 U.S. direct-to-video crime thriller film directed by Malek Akkad in his feature debut and starring Sarah Butler, Malcolm McDowell and D. B. Sweeney. It follows an employee followed by an assassin and locked in an elevator.
Two homies, Smokey and Craig, smoke a dope dealer's weed and try to figure a way to get the $200 they owe to the dealer by 10 p.m. that same night.

Craig and his cousin Day-Day have finally gotten jobs as mall security guards and moved into their own crib. When a fake evil Santa Claus robs their rundown apartment on Christmas Eve, they embark on a comical adventure in an effort to track down the bandit and retrieve their stolen loot.
High school football coach from poor Texas town Odessa aims to get his kids to fight for state championship victory
A group of camp counselors are stalked and murdered by an unknown assailant while trying to reopen a summer camp where, years before, it was the site of a child's drowning and a grisly double murder.
A living snowman and a little girl struggle to elude a greedy magician who is after the snowman's magic hat.
A fearless young princess finding her sister, whose icy powers have trapped their kingdom in an eternal winter. We follow the lyrics of the songs on the screen to sing together.
After a woman miraculously escapes a murder, an Alaskan detective sets out on a search for a serial killer who has been acting undisturbed for 13 years.
A man has had a werewolf curse cast upon him. If he doesn't get rid of it, he turns into a killer werewolf when the moon is full.
The G.I. Joe not only fights against COBRA's deadly enemies, but is also forced to contend with the threat posed by the US government.
Aman is afflicted from birth by a terrible curse, as a result of which all those killed by his gun awaken in the form of the undead.

Get on Up is a 2014 American biographical musical drama film about the life of singer James Brown and directed by Tate Taylor and written by Jez and John-Henry Butterworth. ... The film was released on August 1, 2014.

In Tokyo, yet another earthquake causes a serious accident inside a nuclear power plant during which the wife of Joe Brody, an experienced American supervisor, is killed. The studies on the mysterious case go on for many years, until the professor manages to shed light on the nature of those mysterious tremors.

TITOLO: Godzilla and Mothra: The Battle for Earth
TRAMA: In the midst of another rampage by Godzilla, Mothra emerges to save the human race from Battra.

After being framed, a cowboy is sent to jail. After his time is served, he leaves with vengeance in his heart. Soon he meets a young Native American woman and together they go to settle their score with a small town and its corrupt leader.
A group of friends get together to honor the memory of their basketball coach and realize that maturity doesn't always come with age.
Lenny Feder returns with his family to his hometown to be able to be with his old friends. He soon discovers that he hasn't left the crazy life of Los Angeles behind.
Two Pittsburgh boxers, champions and fierce ring rivals across the nation, decide to fight to the hilt in the last fight.

An action-packed, epic space adventure, Marvel's "Guardians of the Galaxy," expands the Marvel Cinematic Universe into the cosmos, where brash adventurer Peter Quill finds himself the object of an unrelenting bounty hunt after stealing a mysterious orb coveted by Ronan, a powerful villain with ambitions that threaten the entire universe. To evade the ever-persistent Ronan, Quill is forced into an uneasy truce with a quartet of disparate misfits--Rocket, a gun-toting raccoon; Groot, a tree-like humanoid; the deadly and enigmatic Gamora; and the revenge-driven Drax the Destroyer. But when Quill discovers the true power of the orb and the menace it poses to the cosmos, he must do his best to rally his ragtag rivals for a last, desperate stand--with the
John Hancock is an alcoholic and unpopular superhero who causes massive damage every time he steps up against crime. Ray Embrey decides to help him to revive the image of him.

Hanna, a sixteen-year-old girl, becomes a perfect hitman thanks to the training given to her by her father, who has a risky mission in Europe in store for her. The young woman, however, begins to wonder about her own destiny.
The Henderson family adopt a friendly Sasquatch but have a hard time trying to keep the legend of 'Bigfoot' a secret.
Four naive Americans, in need of easy cash, decide to fly to Colombia and raid the safe of a notorious drug lord with connections to the corrupt military regime.
Hitch, known as Doctor Trailer, helps men conquer the women they are in love with. One day, however, he too ends up involved in a relationship that puts him in serious trouble.
A curious youngster moves to Salem, where he struggles to fit in before awakening a trio of diabolical witches that were executed in the 17th century.
An eight-year-old troublemaker must protect his house from a pair of burglars when he is accidentally left home alone by his family during Christmas vacation.

TITOLO: Home Alone 2: Lost in New York
TRAMA: One year after Kevin McCallister (Macaulay Culkin) was left home alone and had to defeat a pair of bumbling burglars, he accidentally finds himself stranded in New York City - and the same criminals are not far behind.

A pacularly clumsy group of criminals try to pass a microchip through airport security checks but lose the stolen property inside a toy car belonging to the elderly Mrs. Hess. The men follow the unsuspecting woman to her home and watch her as she gives the model to little Alex Pruitt.
Little Kevin wants to reunite his separated parents before the holidays. To do this, he uses all his wits.
Phil Brocker is a DEA agent in deep crisis since, during an action against a gang of bikers, he had the son of a boss killed who swore revenge. Phil, recently widowed, decides to retire.
In 1906, in China, a British anthropologist discovers a frozen prehistoric creature and must transport it to Europe by train.
A policeman is transferred to the countryside, but the rural reality is more gruesome than expected, and violent death seems to be present everywhere.

Hot Tub Time Machine follows a group of best friends who've become bored with their adult lives: Adam has been dumped by his girlfriend; Lou is a party guy who can't find the party; Nick's wife controls his every move; and video game-obsessed Jacob won't leave his basement.

Cindy Lou is a little girl who lives in the village of Chinonso and, near the celebrations for the arrival of Christmas, convinces the village mayor to invite the Grinch, a grumpy and wicked being fantastic, who lives with the objects taken from the landfill.
New York, 2012. A mysterious virus killed men and turned them into vampires. The only human who survived the infection is Dr. Robert Neville, who desperately struggles to find a cure.

In the year 2035, technology and robots are now part of everyday life. Investigator Del Spooner must investigate the murder of Dr. Alfred Lanning, a U.S. scientist. Robotics, in which Sonny seems to be involved. But that would mean a violation of the Three Basic Laws.
Two centuries after being created by Doctor Frankenstein, Adam is once again involved in a war between two immortal races.

Sandy Bigelow Patterson spends a perfect life in Colorado, with a wife, two children and good professional success, when he discovers that a woman in Florida has stolen his identity and uses his accounts to enjoy a life of luxury and wildness.

Jeff Cole is a recent graduate of the Cincinnati police academy who dreams of working undercover. His wish is granted and through success is given the task of taking down state-wide crack dealer Dwayne Gittens aka "God".

The film tells of an imaginary and almost successful alien invasion of Earth, with the destruction of several iconic monuments of the United States of America, such as the Empire State Building, the White House and the Library Tower in Los Angeles. A huge advertising campaign was used to launch the film, which began during the 30th edition of the Super Bowl final.

When offered four thousand dollars to break into a computer network, Leon and Greg are not concerned with something as petty as morality. The only real questions are what complications can arise from hacking into a small home business, what is wrong with the twenty year old daughter Madison. What should Greg do when his friend cannot stop watching the girl on her own webcam, without her knowledge.

Four men and a woman dressed as house painters raid the Manhattan Trust and take about fifty people between customers and bank employees hostage, forcing them to wear overalls and masks. Investigator Keith Frazier has the task of negotiating with the chief of the criminals, Dalton Russell, who has studied his plan in detail.

Moving to a new home, family members find themselves forced to make drastic decisions when they realize that they are being persecuted by evil spirits that haunt the place and who have taken possession of the body of one of the children.
After surviving an unexpected attack in enemy territory, industrialist Tony Stark builds high-tech armor and vows to protect the world as Iron Man.
Now that the whole world knows the true identity of Iron Man, millionaire inventor Tony Stark faces pressures to collaborate with the military and form new alliances to face a powerful enemy.
After saving New York from destruction and remaining sleepless and worried since then, Tony Stark left without armor must fight his inner fears to defeat his new enemy, the Mandarin.
Because of an unusual disorder that has aged him four times faster than a typical human being, a boy looks like a 40-year-old man as he starts fifth grade at public school after being homeschooled.

In what was meant as a harmless birthday prank, three of Reagan High School's most popular girls, Julie, Marcie, and Courtney pretend to kidnap their friend, the latter shoving a jawbreaker into the victim's mouth to keep her from screaming.

TITOLO: Jay and Silent Bob Strike Back
TRAMA: Jay and Silent Bob Strike Back is a tale of adventure on the open road. When Dante and Randal (of Clerks fame) get a restraining order to keep the punchy Jay and his hetero life-mate, Silent Bob, from selling drugs in front of the Quick Stop convenience store, their lives are suddenly empty.
Jimmy Carr's show at the Apollo Theater in London, where the comedian spreads jokes of notable perfidy without ever getting upset.
A father vows to get his son a Turbo Man action figure for Christmas. However, every store is sold out of them, and he must travel all over town and compete with everybody else in order to find one.
John Wick (2014) An ex-hit-man comes out of retirement to track down the gangsters that killed his dog and took everything from him.

A black soldier returns from fighting for the Union in the Civil War only to find out that his mother has been murdered by a gang of white thugs. He becomes a bounty hunter, determined to track down and kill the men who killed his mother.

Summaries. Four inner-city teenagers get caught up in the pursuit of power and happiness, which they refer to as "the juice". 4 Harlem teens, Q, Bishop, Raheem and Steel, are out skipping school one day when they find out an old friend was killed in a shootout at a bar.
When two kids find and play a magical board game, they release a man trapped in it for decades--and a host of dangers that can only be stopped by finishing the game.
A crazy woman who lives in an old mansion thinks she's with her brother/lover, who lures victims to her.
Kevin Hart: Let Me Explain is a 2013 American stand-up comedy film featuring Kevin Hart's 2012 performance at Madison Square Garden. It was released in theaters on July 3, 2013.
Dave, together with Mindy, creates the world's first superhero team. Unfortunately, however, Hit Girl is exposed and forced to retire.

Phil Weston is a calm man with healthy values; from an early age, however, he had to suffer the intrusiveness of his father, Buck, who has always focused on competitiveness. Now the man finds himself coaching the football team in which his son Sam also plays and realizes that he looks a lot like his parent.
Killa Season is a 2006 drama film directed to the video about a rapper's youthful life as a crook.
After retiring to a hut in a remote and inhospitable area of the Appalachian Mountains to forget the horrors of the war, an ex-soldier receives a visit from a Serbian soldier in search of revenge.

When Dr. Frankenstein is killed by a monster he created, his daughter and his lab assistant Marshall continue his experiments. The two fall in love and attempt to transplant Marshall's brain in to the muscular body of a retarded servant Stephen, in order to prolong the aging Marshall's life. Meanwhile, the first monster seeks revenge on the grave robbers who sold the body parts used in its creation to Dr. Frankenstein. Soon it comes after Marshall and the doctor's daughter.
Dr. Marshall is sucked, together with his two children, into a space-time vortex that takes you back in time.

Billy, Paddy, Archie and Sam, have been best friends since childhood. By now aged, the four go to Las Vegas for the bachelor party of one of them, but here they face the changing times and the problems given by their age.
A man is shocked when he learns that the man who killed his wife and daughter has received a mild sentence.

TITOLO: Lego Star Wars: The Yoda Chronicles
TRAMA: With Padwan's help, Yoda leads the Jedi in a fight to stop Darth and his followers. We follow the adventures of Star Wars in Lego version.
Born on the original Christmas in the stable next door to Jesus Christ, Brian of Nazareth spends his life being mistaken for a messiah.
The Looney Tunes search for a man's missing father and the mythical Blue Monkey diamond.
The president of the United States recruits former federal agent Machete to take out an eccentric arms dealer who plans to spread war and anarchy around the world.
While organizing the family reunion, a miarch has to deal with other dramas, including her granddaughter with a troubled love.

Madea's Neighbor From Hell is an American comedy stage play, written, directed, produced by, and stars Tyler Perry. It also stars Cassi Davis, and Rhonda Davis. It was released by Lionsgate, on DVD, on April 22, 2014.
Maleficent to Diaval. Maleficent is a powerful fairy and is the main character of Disney's Maleficent. Her dead parents were royalty and king and queen of the Moors.
All Brad wants is to shoot Malibu with his friends and compose rap songs. For a boy from the most elegant Pacific beaches, however, it is very difficult to gain credibility in the sector.

The genesis of Superman, which comes to Earth from the still-born planet Krypton. Lovingly raised by the spouses Kent, Superman discovers his extraordinary powers during adolescence and decides to secretly put them at the service of others.
A boy with an excellent talent in tai chi manages to enter, thanks to his skills, the world of combat.

Thomas A. Anderson works at Metacortex as a software programmer. During the day he is known to be a model citizen, selfless and law-abiding, while at night he lives a second life, as an active hacker, under the pseudonym of "Neo", and in this capacity he has committed practically every possible cyber crime. Watched by Agents Smith, Brown and Jones, he is arrested and a bedbug inserted into his body to follow him. One night, a series of cryptic sentences appear on Anderson's monitor about something called the "Matrix": eager to know what it is, he accepts a request for contact from Trinity, expert hacker right hand of the mysterious Morpheus, who leads him to him. after having eradicated the bug. Neo asks to know more about their work and they offer to reveal the real world they live in (a choice symbolized by a "red pill"). After ingesting the pill, he wakes up abruptly, naked, immersed in a viscous liquid from an incubator, with his body connected to electric cables, realizing that he is inside one of many huge circular towers that house billions of incubators containing human beings.

Six months after Neo's transformation into the Chosen, the rebellious humans continue to fight against the machines, for the ultimate liberation of the human species. Led by Neo himself, they sense the escalation of the battle when they discover the machines' plans to destroy Zion (in the center of the Earth) by blasting their way with drills. A general order is issued to return to Zion to stop the advance of the machines in the outside world, but those who believe in the Chosen ignore the order and keep out of the citadel to be able to constantly connect to the Matrix, in the hope of important communications from the Oracle.

Morpheus understands that the One is actually a control system devised by the architects of the Matrix. As Zion's army battles the sentries and the machines, Neo and Trinity decide to challenge the enemy in their heart, the City of Machines.
Meet the Browns (2008) A single mom takes her family to Georgia for the funeral of her father -- a man she never met. There, her clan is introduced to the crass, fun-loving Brown family.

Two agents have a very special assignment: to control the activity of aliens residing on Earth and to make sure that their presence remains hidden from the eyes of other human beings. Furthermore, J and K must stop an intergalactic terrorist who wants to kill the ambassadors of the enemy galaxies as soon as possible.
Planet Earth is under threat from Serleena, an alien entity that looks like an underwear model. Agent J plans to stop her, she cannot succeed without K's help, but she has decided to retire.

Intergalactic criminal Boris the Animal escapes from the LunarMax prison, located on the Moon, with the intent to go back in time and eliminate Agent K, responsible for arresting him and amputating his arm.
Carl Brashear promises his father to join the Navy. Unfortunately, when he does, he is only granted three possibilities: to be a cook, an attendant or to give up.
A young street hustler attempts to escape the rigors and temptations of the ghetto in a quest for a better life.
A young woman goes searching for her missing ast father. Her journey takes her to a strange Californian seaside town governed by a mysterious undead cult.
Santa Claus and his favourite deer stuck on the apex of high mountain, Mickey and Donald hurry for help.

In the famous animated version of the Christmas classic written by Charles Dickens, the Christmas spirits of the past, present and future go to visit the elderly and terribly stingy Ebenezer Scrooge, to make him understand what the true spirit of Christmas is.

TITOLO: Mickey's Magical Christmas: Snowed in at the House of Mouse
TRAMA: The Christmas evening has just ended in the Mouse Club, but the snow blocks the door and nobody can go out anymore. Minnie remedies old videotapes with Christmas themed cartoons. Meanwhile Donald Duck does not feel the spirit of Christmas and his friends try to make him come. After the interviews and yet another gift, Donald Duck continues to ignore Christmas, until Mickey, on the advice of the Talking Cricket, asks a star for everyone to celebrate Christmas. Donald finally wishes happy holidays to all and the feature ends with Mickey's short Christmas carol.
Gag and fun in this classic with five Christmas themed episodes that bring together the great characters who wrote the story of Disney.

Monstroid is an 1980s American monster film directed by Kenneth Hartford. It was originally titled Monster when the film was first announced in 1975 and again in 1977, and underwent numerous cast changes.
Japanese animated adaptation of Marvel's "The Monster of Frankenstein" comic book series.
The rivalry between Mike and Sulley dates back to the time of university, when both were kicked out of the Professional Scarers program.
After several locals are viciously murdered, a Louisiana sheriff starts to suspect he may be dealing with a werewolf.
Mr. Peabody is a genius although he is a dog. Using a time machine, he and his friends experience the great historical events firsthand.
After a bitter divorce, an actor disguises himself as a female housekeeper to spend time with his children held in custody by his former wife.
When two girls move to the country to be near their ailing mother, they have adventures with the wondrous forest spirits who live nearby.
A Vietnam vet terrorizes a house full of nurses.
A clumsy teenager with a strange family helps a friend become class president against a popular student.

Need for Speed (2014) Fresh from prison, a street racer who was framed by a wealthy business associate joins a cross country race with revenge in mind. His ex-partner, learning of the plan, places a massive bounty on his head as the race begins.
A crime lord ascends to power and becomes megalomaniacal while a maverick police detective vows to stop him.
The streets of Newark, NJ are the setting for this stark drama of two teenagers who decide to carjack for fun and profit - but soon find themselves the target of every cop in town.
Next Friday (2000) Uncle Elroy and Day Day owe money on taxes so Craig finds a way to steal from the next door neighbors to pay off the taxes so Uncle Elroy's house doesn't get put up for auction.

TITOLO: Nightmare on Elm Street 5  The Dream Child
TRAMA: The pregnant Alice finds Freddy Krueger striking through the sleeping mind of her unborn child, hoping to be reborn into the real world.

Nobody Needs to Know is a story of Fame and the towns and industries and the people who create it and support it. It's the story of two actresses on divergent paths who unwittingly illustrate the power of Fame and its ability to pursue those who run from it and run from those who pursue it. Aesthetically. it's an alchemy of Nathaniel West's The Day of the Locust, The Shadow radio serial, Ralph Ellison's The Invisible Man, and Juergen Teller's Go-See's mixed and sampled to create a sublime cinematic Paul's Boutique for the Era of the Image and beyond.

is a 2016 American neo-noir psychological thriller film written, produced and directed by Tom Ford, based on the 1993 novel Tony and Susan by Austin Wright. ... Nocturnal Animals was selected to compete for the Golden Lion at the 73rd Venice International Film Festival, where it won the Grand Jury Prize.

Non-Stop is a 2014 action thriller film directed by Jaume Collet-Serra and starring Liam Neeson and Julianne Moore. It follows a Federal Air Marshal who must find a killer on an international flight after receiving texts saying a passenger will be executed every 20 minutes until financial demands are met.

A team of the most skilled illusionists in the world, known as The Four Horsemen, during its television broadcast manages to rob a bank in Paris. The case is being handled by FBI agents Dylan and Interpol's Alma.
Three men in their thies are determined to relive college's carefree years and overcome love disappointments. To do this, they decide to found a brotherhood outside the university campus.
A terrible threat hangs over the United States. Relieved of office after the First Lady's death, an agent is fighting to save the President's life.

Ex-Special Forces soldier Louis Stevens returns to Miami to find his former high school overrun by drugs and violence. A master of the Brazilian maal art, capoeira, Stevens pledges to straighten out a dozen of the school's worst students by teaching them this demanding and highly-disciplined fighting style. Slowly, his program begins to work, giving the students new hope and purpose. But the local drug lord, himself a maal arts expert, vows to stop Stevens' positive influence. Now Stevens must fight to save his own life, as well as the lives of his rebellious young students.
When their third child Jessica comes to life lifeless Kate and John decide to adopt a Russian child to overcome the trauma.

In 2013, a mysterious breach appears on the bottom of the Pacific Ocean. The breach is an interdimensional portal from which giant alien monsters, known as Kaij, emerge. The war waged against these creatures is destined to destroy millions of lives and consume human resources for years to come. To face the titanic threats, the nations of the world decide to put aside their enmities. Special weapons are devised: huge mechas called Jaegers, usually controlled simultaneously by two pilots whose minds are connected to a neural network. Since the devastating attacks of the Kaij are almost all focused on the states bordering the Pacific, the most powerful nations of the Pacific Rim are using a large part of their resources to join the Jaeger project and their development.

A young man from Harlem, forced to cope with the 1980s drug scene, builds an illegal empire, only to have a crisis of conscience. Ace is an impressionable young man working for a dry cleaning business. His friend, drug dealer Mitch goes to prison. In an unrelated incident, he finds some cocaine in a pants pocket.
After tragedy strikes, a grieving father discovers an ancient burial ground behind his home with the power to raise the dead.
A teenage boy and his father move to his recently-deceased mother's hometown, where they encounter the ancient Native American cemetery with the power to raise the dead.
Rushed to an unknown planet, a pilot realizes that he is in a primitive place, where apes reign, and where men fight for survival, persecuted and enslaved by primate tyrants.
Ash Ketchum must gather the three spheres of fire, ice and lightning in order to restore balance to the Orange Islands.
In 79 BC, during the eruption of Pompeii, a gladiator tries to return home as soon as possible, despite the rain of lava and debris, in order to save the woman he loves.

Pootie Tang, the musician/actor/folk hero of the ghetto, is chronicled from his early childhood to his battles against the evil Corporate America, who try to steal his magic belt and make him sell out by endorsing addictive products to his people.
A team of commandos on a mission in a Central American jungle find themselves hunted by an extraterrestrial warrior.

In a town in the American province, two girls disappear. Keller, the father of one of them, is convinced that the culprit is a young man from the neighborhood and decides to kidnap him to make him confess by force. Meanwhile, investigator Loki, stubbornly committed to the case, is on the trail of another suspect.
Three high school students want to organize a memorable birthday party that will raise their low popularity with schoolmates and attract girls.
A group of scientists is traveling to a distant planet in search of the origins of man. However, astronauts come into contact with an entity that could cause the extinction of the human race.

Pup is an uplifting story about a dog willing to do whatever it takes to become the greatest sheepdog of all time - even if that means flying to the moon! The adorable and zany animals he meets before - and after lift-off make for an out-of-this-world adventure families will enjoy for light years to come.
Nick, after losing his life, finds himself in an office of the Rest in Peace Department, a celestial agency that recruits deceased agents to return them to Earth in different bodies.

Remy, a Parisian mouse, dreams of becoming a great chef in order to offer everyone his delicious recipes. When he ends up in the basement of one of the most renowned restaurants in the city, the rodent decides to stay there and learn to cook.
A new Mothra takes to the air and must battle Death Ghidora to save humanity.
Rebirth of Mothra II (1997) Mothra's twin nymphs and children from the city find a lost city, as well as a giant monster that is attracted to environmental calamities.

TITOLO: Return of the Kung Fu Dragon
TRAMA: Golden City, capital of wondrous Phoenix island, is attacked by an evil despot and his sorcerer ally and conquered, with the Emperor and his three generals killed by the invaders. The young princess and the three children of the generals are hidden away from the invaders with the hope that they one day will return to avenge the deaths of their fathers and reclaim the island paradise. Almost twenty years pass and the grown children do finally return to confront the despot and the sorcerer but, will they be successful?

TITOLO: Return to Cabin by the Lake
TRAMA: Two years after being presumed dead, Stanley Caldwell (under the alias of "Alan") meets with an agent named Lauren on a boat to discuss a new screenplay. They soon learn that despite public protest, director Mike Helton has begun principal photography on Cabin by the Lake, a film based on Stanley's old screenplay detailing his exploits as a serial killer. Amongst the protesters is Paul Parsons, the brother of Kimberly Parsons who was one of Stanley's last victims. When Lauren confesses to hiring someone to rewrite his screenplay, Stanley binds her to a cement flower pot. A horrified Lauren realizes Alan's true identity and desperately suggests that he become a director. Stanley is intrigued by the idea, but nevertheless pushes her overboard to drown.
Abandoned on a sunburned planet and left for dead, Riddick finds himself battling an alien race of predators. In order to save himself, he must activate an emergency beacon that warns two ships.

Hart, a second-grade teacher, must try to survive a day of forced coexistence with his girlfriend's brother, a policeman who does not see him favorably and does not approve of the union between the two.
Blu and Gioel and their three children leave the comfort of the city and travel to the Amazon jungle to learn to live like real birds.

TITOLO: Rise of the Planet of the Apes
TRAMA: Genetic engineering experiments for the treatment of Alzheimer's create an evolved and intelligent species of monkeys.
The story of the legendary outlaw is portrayed with the characters as humanoid animals.
In 2028, a robotics company sees the possibility of applying its technology to humans by transforming a seriously injured police officer into a cyborg.

Robotix is a 1985 animated series based on the Milton Bradley toy of the same name. The original toy was of the construction type, similar to that of the Meccano and K'nex, which included engines, wheels and calipers.

TITOLO: Rogue One: A Star Wars Story
TRAMA: From Lucasfilm comes the first of the Star Wars standalone films, "Rogue One: A Star Wars Story," an all-new epic adventure. In a time of conflict, a group of unlikely heroes band together on a mission to steal the plans to the Death Star, the Empire's ultimate weapon of destruction.

Rules Don't Apply is a 2016 American romantic comedy-drama film written, produced and directed by Warren Beatty. ... Set in 1958 Hollywood, the film follows the romantic relationship between a young actress and her driver, which is forbidden by their employer, Howard Hughes.
A young man visiting and helping his uncle in New York City finds himself forced to fight a street gang and the mob with his maal art skills.
A Princeton student becomes the pupil of an online gambling tycoon, whose shady deals drew FBI attention. The boy is forced by the federal agency to collaborate.

The Austrian Niki Lauda and the English James Hunt meet for the first time on the Formula 3 circuits. One is methodical, rational, not particularly nice; the other is a womanizer who enjoys life and runs like there's no tomorrow. Their rivalry becomes historic and marks an incredible season of motoring, made up of indelible dramas and miraculous resumptions.
CIA agent Tobin Frost, guilty of deseon, is captured by his former colleagues and interrogated in a secret refuge. A terrorist attack, however, reverses the situation

TITOLO: Santa and the Ice Cream Bunny
TRAMA: When Santa's sleigh gets stuck in Florida, he tells a group of kids the story of Thumbelina.

In 1961, the author Pamela "P. L." Travers reluctantly travels from his London home to Los Angeles to work with Walt Disney at the urging of his agent, Diarmuid Russell. Disney has pursued film rights for its Mary Poppins stories for twenty years, having promised his daughters that he would produce a film based on them. Travers firmly resisted Disney's efforts because he feared what he would do to his character. However, not having written books for a while, the writer risks losing her home. Still, Russell must remind her that Disney has accepted two important clauses - no unprecedented animation and script approval - before she agrees to go.
Two men wake up chained in a room and find a lifeless body in the center of that space. An unknown voice deploys them, with no way out, against each other.

Jigsaw has fled again and continues to terrify the whole community with its deadly puzzles. This time her focus is on Dr. Lynn Delon, kidnapped and forced to find a cure that prevents cancer from killing him.

Jigsaw has fled again and continues to terrify the whole community with its deadly puzzles. This time her focus is on Dr. Lynn Delon, kidnapped and forced to find a cure that prevents cancer from killing him.

The death of the Riddler and the disciple Amanda were not enough to put an end to their diabolical criminal plan. The two detectives who followed the investigation, Rigg and Hoffman, fell into the net this time.
Seth Baxter, a murderer who escaped the law, is trapped in one of the Riddler's diabolical machines. Agent Strahm also soon finds himself in the same situation.
Between lethal choices and cruel gimmicks, Riddler finds his next victim in William Easton, an insurer who has a client's death on his conscience.

Saw: The Final Chapter (2010) As a deadly battle rages over Jigsaw's brutal legacy, a group of Jigsaw survivors gathers to seek the support of self-help guru and fellow survivor Bobby Dagen, a man whose own dark secrets unleash a new wave of terror.

School Dance is a 2014 American musical comedy-drama film directed, co-written and produced by Nick Cannon. The film stars Bobb'e J. Thompson, The Ranger $, Mike Epps, Luenell, Kristina DeBarge, Katt Williams, Tiffany Haddish, George Lopez and Wilmer Valderrama.
In 1976 a singer uses the profits from his only hit to buy a basketball team that is in danger of failing when the ABA and the NBA merge.
A man with a difficult secret must redeem himself by changing the lives of seven strangers, including the woman he fell in love with.
Cool black private eye John Shaft is hired by a crime lord to find and retrieve his kidnapped daughter.

The movie is about Sita, the Hindu Goddess from the epic "The Ramayana", who accompanies Lord Rama on a 14 year exile in forest. Sita is abducted by Ravana, the ruler of Lanka. This movie tells the story of Rama and Sita, along-with a biographical account of the director's relationship with her husband.
Vigilante Slaughter comes under attack from Duncan, a local money launderer whose hit-man traps Slaughter in a car at a cliff, but Slaughter escapes, arms himself, and goes after Duncan's hideout.
A Colorado ski resort is besieged by a sub-human beast that commits brutal murders on the slopes.

SOBAKA is the thrilling story of a lonely Russian immigrant trying to find the "American dream" in present day Los Angeles. To provide care for his dying sister he works as an assistant to a mysterious and dangerous man, but his desire to achieve something more takes him down a dark and risky path
South Central (1992) A former gangster fresh out of prison wants to change his life for the better and must save his 10 year old son whose already chosen a gang life.

TITOLO: Spacehunter: Adventures in the Forbidden Zone
TRAMA: On a distant planet inhabited by mutants, two bounty-hunters race to rescue three Earth female captives from the clutches of an evil mutant warlord.
Egyptologist Erica Baron finds more than she bargained for during her long-planned trip to The Land of the Pharoahs: murder, theft, betrayal, love, and a mummy's curse.
The life of student Peter Parker is turned upside down by the arrival of dangerous new opponents. As Spider-Man, he must protect his loved ones and the city of New York from this lethal threat.

In order to pay for their holidays, the students Candy, Faith, Brit and Cotty decide to rob a fast food restaurant. When they end up in jail, the trafficker Alien manages to get them out, but in return he wants the girls to work for him.
Captain Kirk is suspended from command of the Enterprise and separated from First Officer Spock. A threatening force on the horizon forces the Federation to retrace its steps.

TITOLO: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
TRAMA: Thanks to the teachings of an elderly Jedi master, young Anakin Skywalker learns to master the incredible powers of the Force.

TITOLO: Star Wars: Episode II - Attack of the Clones
TRAMA: Obi-Wan Kenobi and his apprentice Anakin Skywalker are tasked with protecting the Republic from a separatist movement that threatens its existence.

TITOLO: Star Wars: Episode III - Revenge of the Sith
TRAMA: Seduced by the dark side of the Force, Anakin Skywalker rebels against his mentor, Obi Wan Kenobi, and assumes the identity of the fearsome tyrant Dart Vader.

TITOLO: Star Wars: Episode IV - A New Hope
TRAMA: Luke Skywalker lived and worked on his uncle's farm on the remote planet of Tatooineand he was bored beyond belief. He yearned for adventures out among the stars, adventures that would take him beyond the farthest galaxies to distant and alien worlds.

TITOLO: Star Wars: Episode V - The Empire Strikes Back
TRAMA: Master Yoda prepares young Luke Skywalker to face the terrible tyrant Dart Vader, who is about to launch a devastating attack to crush the rebels.

TITOLO: Star Wars: Episode VI  Return of the Jedi
TRAMA: After a daring mission to rescue Han Solo from Jabba the Hutt, the Rebels dispatch to Endor to destroy the second Death Star. Meanwhile, Luke struggles to help Darth Vader back from the dark side without falling into the Emperor's trap.

The genesis of Superman, who comes to Earth from the infant planet Krypton. Lovingly raised by the Kents, Superman discovers his extraordinary powers in his teens and decides to secretly put them at the service of others.

Immediately after reconciling with his ex-wife Lenore, Bryan Mills sees his life turn into a nightmare when the woman is brutally murdered. The man is also unfairly accused of the murder and his reaction is to use his anger to carry out an ocious revenge against the real criminals and protect the last thing in the world that remains: the daughter.

TITOLO: Talladega Nights: The Ballad of Ricky Bobby
TRAMA: When a French driver sets his record, Ricky Bobby, the greatest driver in NASCAR history, is forced to go back to fourth in order not to lose everything he has.

Flynn Rider is a charming bandit who, thanks to his good looks, loose talk and a fair amount of luck, has always had an easy life. Rapunzel, on the other hand, is a beautiful and extravagant girl with splendid golden hair, over twenty meters long, who lives imprisoned in a very tall tower. One day, while fleeing the authorities, Flynn finds shelter right in the tower where Rapunzel is confined.
As the first wedding anniversary approaches, Jane remembers the exciting twelve months she spent with Tarzan.
Four teenage mutant ninja turtles emerge from the shadows to protect New York City from a gang of criminal ninjas.

TITOLO: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles II: The Secret of the Ooze
TRAMA: The Turtles and the Shredder battle once again, this time for the last canister of the ooze that created the Turtles, with which Shredder wants to unleash an army of new mutants.
The four Ninja Turtles are found in seventeenth-century Japan with the help of a magic scepter to rescue April, considered a witch to be fought.

Wooden puppet Pinocchio is brought to life with the assistance of a fairy. His wish is to become a real boy. His creator, Geppetto the woodcarver, tries to teach the boy about acting responsibly. Pinocchio has many adventures that provide him the valuable lessons he needs to learn about life before he can become a real boy. Lying proves to be a pacular problem.

A convicted strangler, studying the paranormal in his jail cell, learns to make himself invisible. As an invisible man, he escapes from prison to stalk and strangle the five women who testified against him at his trial. Robert Foxworth plays the police lieutenant assigned to protect them, and to catch the invisible strangler.

A black high school student is caught dating a white girl by the girl's brother. He and his biker gang beat the boy to death. The boy's brother, who is a member of a black biker gang, hears about it and comes to town to avenge his brother's death.

Detective Robert Malone (Fred Williamson) is a tough member of the NYPD who seems to make his own rules. . Official Website: Facebook: A lone cop struggles to protect a female photographer from a gang of . Trailer del film d' azione Black Cobra con Fred Williamson, Eva Grimaldi, Karl Landgreen, Sabrina Siani.

J.J., a rising star in the black crime scene, is in the process of consolidating his power over the neighborhood. One of the only remaining obstacles is the white heroin cartel that is understandably reluctant to abandon such a lucrative market. Tensions rise between the two rivals, and people on both sides get killed. Eventually, the matter is destined to come to an explosive confrontation.
A research vessel finds a missing ship, commanded by a mysterious scientist, on the edge of a black hole.
Shy Marc and the insignificant Rebecca, teenagers obsessed with fame, use the means given by the Internet to find out where celebrities live and to steal from their homes.

New York. Following yet another heinous murder committed by a serial murderer, Agent Lincoln Rhyme begins investigations. Ruthless and at the same time enigmatic, the case puts the murder team in serious difficulty.
The world has been destroyed by an apocalyptic event and the human race is in grave danger. Only one man, thanks to a prophetic book, is able to save all human beings.
Two Irish brothers improvise executioners to clear Boston of crime. A detective tries to stop them.

TITOLO: The Boy in the Plastic Bubble
TRAMA: The girl next door makes a teen born with immune deficiencies want to leave his germ-free bubble.
A police receptionist receives a phone call from a girl locked up in a trunk. So he has to deal with a psychopath whom he has already known, if he wants to save the girl's life.

The Chinese Room is an award-winning 2009 independent feature. It was shot on location in Washington, DC with an all-local cast and crew. It is a self-financed thriller inspired by the famous thought experiment by John Searle.
Forced to live underground, the survivors of an ice age seek another outpost where they can establish themselves.
The warnings of a climatologist about the imminent arrival of a new ice age are ignored. But when a storm of biblical propoons hits New York, the end of humanity seems inevitable
Five friends travel to a cabin in the woods, where they unknowingly release flesh-possessing demons.
When a 12 year-old girl is possessed by a mysterious entity, her mother seeks the help of two priests to save her.
Mafia family in the witness protection program is moved to a French city and has several problems adapting to new life.
A man, framed for a crime he didn't commit, escapes from prison and kidnaps a young woman in a sports car. The fugitive hopes to make it to Mexico before being captured.
In the colorful future, a cab driver unwittingly becomes the central figure in the search for a legendary cosmic weapon to keep Evil and Mr. Zorg at bay.
Two childhood friends find themselves forced to become enemies.

TITOLO: The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo
TRAMA: This English-language adaptation of the Swedish novel by Stieg Larsson follows a disgraced journalist, Mikael Blomkvist (Daniel Craig), as he investigates the disappearance of a wealthy piarch's niece from 40 years ago. He is aided by the pierced, tattooed, punk computer hacker named Lisbeth Salander (Rooney Mara).
